Learn more about the life insurance and death benefits available to Service members and their families.
The Department of Defense (DoD) and the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA), along with other agencies, provide comprehensive assistance and support to the survivors of fallen Service members and veterans. This video provides a brief overview of the most common survivor benefits available to family members.
